org.dellroad.jibxbindings

Interface XMLEnum

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AccountStatus, AccountType, AnswerType, APIVersion, CallDirection, CallStatus, ConferenceStatus, Language, RejectReason, SMSDirection, SMSStatus, TranscriptionStatus, TranscriptionType, Voice

    public interface XMLEnum
    Implemented by Enums whose values' XML representations are different from their names. To make use of this interface, specify enum-value-method="getXMLName" in the JiBX binding file.

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      String getXMLName()
      Get the unique string to use to represent this instance in an XML file.
